					span.mono inline monospace
			tr
				td
					| [code]language
					br
					| int main() {...}
					br
					| [/code]
				td
					span.code int main() {...}
			tr
				td
					pre
						| [code]aa
						| ∧＿∧
						| ( ・ω・) Let's try that again.
						| [&#x2F;code]
				td
					pre.aa
						| ∧＿∧
